Awak kata, saya terkenal
di Istana Qing Chi?

41
00:03:01,574 --> 00:03:02,534
Tentulah.

42
00:03:03,174 --> 00:03:04,653
Semua cerita yang
kami dengar setiap hari

43
00:03:04,894 --> 00:03:06,013
