44
00:03:06,373 --> 00:03:08,894
Melawati puteri di Istana Syurga
dalam keadaan mabuk.

45
00:03:09,133 --> 00:03:11,453
Bunuh semua gadis cantik
dengan sebilah pedang di Laut Utara...

46
00:03:11,453 --> 00:03:12,693
Baiklah.

47
00:03:13,133 --> 00:03:14,453
