Tiada otakkah?

114
00:05:56,254 --> 00:05:57,414
Adakah bunga ini ditanam untuk dipetik?

115
00:06:00,254 --> 00:06:00,734
Saya...

116
00:06:01,173 --> 00:06:03,134
Saya akan cari benih untuk dia.

117
00:06:09,493 --> 00:06:10,454
Dungu.

118
00:06:14,294 --> 00:06:16,694
Kini, Qing Mu telah
mendapat Lembing Tai Chang,

119
00:06:17,333 --> 00:06:20,173
dia layak dapat gelaran
Betara Paling Hebat di Puak Betara.

120
00:06:20,574 --> 00:06:22,854
Apa pendapat tuanku terhadap dia?

121
00:06:23,254 --> 00:06:24,493
Menurut Dewa Bapa awak,

122
00:06:25,373 --> 00:06:26,613
awak sukakan dia.

123
00:06:27,734 --> 00:06:30,613
Anakanda hanya sukakan dia,

124
00:06:31,534 --> 00:06:34,254
hanya ingin berteman dengan dia
dan bersatu hati dengan dia

125
00:06:34,893 --> 00:06:35,893
sepanjang hayat ini.

126
00:06:38,893 --> 00:06:41,814
Ada ramai betara di Alam Kayangan
yang sukakan awak,

127
00:06:42,414 --> 00:06:43,854
mengapa awak pilih dia?

128
00:06:44,254 --> 00:06:46,814
Sejak kecil, anakanda ialah
puteri Istana Syurga.

129
00:06:47,333 --> 00:06:48,814
Semua betara mengampu

130
00:06:49,014 --> 00:06:50,814
atau takut pada patik

131
00:06:51,613 --> 00:06:52,574
kecuali Qing Mu.

132
00:06:53,254 --> 00:06:55,493
Dia tak pernah rendah diri
di depan patik.

133
00:06:56,294 --> 00:06:59,014
Dia menceritakan kisah dia mengembara
di tiga alam kepada abang ngah

134
00:06:59,694 --> 00:07:00,653
dan seolah-olah ia berlaku
di depan mata.

135
00:07:01,933 --> 00:07:03,974
Anakanda sukakan sifat dia
yang tabah dan bebas ini.

136
00:07:04,254 --> 00:07:05,173
Suatu hari nanti,

137
00:07:05,493 --> 00:07:07,773
harap kami boleh mengembara
di tiga alam bersama-sama

138
00:07:08,093 --> 00:07:09,893
dan jadi pasangan kekasih yang bahagia.

139
00:07:10,373 --> 00:07:12,014
Namun, cinta yang dipaksa
takkan bahagia.

140
00:07:12,414 --> 00:07:13,493
Khabarnya,

141
00:07:13,854 --> 00:07:15,254
Hou Chi telah bawa dia pergi.

142
00:07:15,534 --> 00:07:17,014
Jangan percaya pada desas-desus.

143
00:07:18,974 --> 00:07:21,333
Anakanda percaya, di tiga alam,
selain abang ngah,

144
00:07:21,534 --> 00:07:22,933
anakanda paling rapat dengan dia.

145
00:07:23,294 --> 00:07:25,134
Dulu, dia tak pernah dekati perempuan.

146
00:07:25,814 --> 00:07:28,493
Mungkin Hou Chi
telah gunakan sihir syaitan

147
00:07:29,014 --> 00:07:30,053
untuk bawa dia pergi.

148
00:07:31,173 --> 00:07:32,134
Tuanku,

149
00:07:32,933 --> 00:07:34,574
anakanda anak kandung tuanku.

150
00:07:35,014 --> 00:07:36,493
Jangan berat sebelah kepada Hou Chi.

151
00:07:38,278 --> 00:07:40,318
Beta tak ambil kisah akan
fikiran Hou Chi.

152
00:07:40,799 --> 00:07:43,679
Beta cuma risau awak rugi
dalam percintaan ini.

153
00:07:45,998 --> 00:07:46,758
Anakanda tahu.

154
00:07:47,278 --> 00:07:48,878
Tuanku kurniai anakanda Payung Yu Hua

155
00:07:48,998 --> 00:07:51,198
kerana harap anakanda takkan
kalah kepada Hou Chi lagi.

156
00:07:52,758 --> 00:07:54,318
Namun, semasa di Bukit Liao Wang
pada hari itu,

157
00:07:54,559 --> 00:07:56,639
Payung Yu Hua seolah-olah
telah terpisah dengan hati anakanda,

158
00:07:57,639 --> 00:08:00,158
pernah ada satu saat yang
ia tak patuh pada arahan anakanda.

159
00:08:00,758 --> 00:08:01,839
Benarkah?

160
00:08:02,119 --> 00:08:02,998
Cepat keluarkannya

161
00:08:03,278 --> 00:08:04,359
dan biar beta tengok.

162
00:08:16,158 --> 00:08:17,559
Saya akan bunuh awak!

163
00:08:18,598 --> 00:08:19,679
Dia?

164
00:08:21,359 --> 00:08:22,278
Kuasa syaitan.

165
00:08:23,038 --> 00:08:23,679
Tuanku,

166
00:08:23,878 --> 00:08:25,359
siapa yang mampu

167
00:08:25,919 --> 00:08:27,639
buat sesuatu pada Payung Yu Hua tuanku?

168
00:08:50,438 --> 00:08:51,559
Kamu keluar dulu.

169
00:08:53,318 --> 00:08:54,278
Ya.

170
00:09:12,815 --> 00:09:17,898
(Istana Chao Sheng)

171
