Sejak Alam Dewa tutup,

172
00:10:35,439 --> 00:10:37,359
Istana Chao Sheng jatuh ke Alam Syurga.

173
00:10:39,559 --> 00:10:41,078
Beta ingat

174
00:10:42,319 --> 00:10:44,559
beta, Mu Guang,

175
00:10:45,359 --> 00:10:47,799
Gu Jun ialah orang terakhir
di Alam Dewa.

176
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:52,559
Tak sangka...

177
00:11:02,638 --> 00:11:03,958
Enam puluh ribu tahun telah berlalu,

178
00:11:05,278 --> 00:11:08,078
Empat Dewa Agung telah dimeterai
selama-lamanya mengikut Alam Dewa.

179
00:11:08,958 --> 00:11:11,038
Biarpun awak Tian Qi, habis?

180
00:11:12,119 --> 00:11:13,559
Di Alam Syurga sekarang,

181
00:11:14,359 --> 00:11:16,239
beta takkan biar awak hidup senang.

182
00:11:29,999 --> 00:11:30,679
Qing Mu.

183
00:11:31,359 --> 00:11:32,319
Mengapa awak di sini?

184
00:11:32,439 --> 00:11:33,239
Di mana Jia Ye?

185
00:11:33,958 --> 00:11:34,879
Saya telah hantar dia pergi dari sini.

186
00:11:35,119 --> 00:11:36,559
Saya ingin sediakan sarapan untuk awak.

187
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:37,679
Semangkuk sup pear.

188
00:11:40,638 --> 00:11:42,158
Tiada buah pear di
Bukit Qi Lian agaknya.

189
00:11:42,319 --> 00:11:43,518
Di mana awak cari buah pear ini?

190
00:11:44,679 --> 00:11:46,158
Saya beli di Alam Manusia
awal pagi tadi.

191
00:11:46,999 --> 00:11:48,199
Luka awak belum sembuh,

192
00:11:48,799 --> 00:11:49,799
tapi, awak tolong saya...

193
00:11:49,799 --> 00:11:50,879
Duduk.

194
00:11:53,199 --> 00:11:53,919
Cara untuk masak

195
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:55,638
sup ini sangat rumit.

196
00:11:56,879 --> 00:11:58,038
Walau boleh guna Ungkapan Api Rohani

197
00:11:58,038 --> 00:11:59,199
untuk mengawal kemarakan apinya,

198
00:11:59,398 --> 00:11:59,799
ini ialah

199
00:11:59,799 --> 00:12:01,439
cara memasak betara.

200
00:12:01,759 --> 00:12:03,239
Kita patut ikut cara Alam Manusia,

201
00:12:03,398 --> 00:12:04,759
mereneh dengan api kecil.

202
00:12:04,958 --> 00:12:06,679
Mereneh dengan perlahan-lahan,

203
00:12:07,038 --> 00:12:09,559
sehingga ia rangup dan lembut,
barulah rasanya sedap.

204
00:12:19,679 --> 00:12:20,638
Mengapa awak tengok saya?

205
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:22,518
Saya tak sangka

206
00:12:23,078 --> 00:12:24,398
selain ada penampilan yang kacak,

207
