pandai bertapa,

208
00:12:29,718 --> 00:12:30,799
awak juga pandai memasak.

209
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:32,759
Taklah.

210
00:12:32,999 --> 00:12:34,158
Saya baru belajarnya.

211
00:12:34,598 --> 00:12:35,799
Sebelum ini, saya buat pau untuk awak,

212
00:12:36,038 --> 00:12:37,638
hampir musnahkan
seluruh Istana Xuan Jing.

213
00:12:40,078 --> 00:12:42,439
Pada masa depan,
tak kira apa yang awak masak,

214
00:12:42,439 --> 00:12:44,038
saya pasti menyokong.

215
00:12:45,559 --> 00:12:46,919
Pada masa depan,
saya hanya akan memasak untuk awak.

216
00:12:51,278 --> 00:12:52,078
Biar saya yang mengipas.

217
00:12:52,158 --> 00:12:52,718
Mari.

218
00:13:19,919 --> 00:13:21,199
Hampir masak, bukan?

219
00:13:21,478 --> 00:13:22,239
Cuba rasakan.

220
00:13:37,398 --> 00:13:38,119
Kenapa?

221
00:13:38,759 --> 00:13:39,518
Tak apa-apa.

222
00:13:41,078 --> 00:13:43,038
Api tak cukup marak.

223
00:13:43,278 --> 00:13:44,398
Kuatkan api.

224
00:14:02,478 --> 00:14:03,598
Siapa? Tunjukkan diri!

225
00:14:09,078 --> 00:14:09,999
Siapa awak?

226
00:14:10,478 --> 00:14:12,078
Tak berani pula tunjukkan muka awak.

227
00:14:14,398 --> 00:14:16,439
Tak sangka Syaitan Zi Yue
dari Alam Syaitan

228
00:14:16,838 --> 00:14:18,838
bersubahat dengan Istana Qing Chi.

229
00:14:20,119 --> 00:14:21,078
Memandangkan awak dah datang,

230
00:14:21,598 --> 00:14:22,958
singgahlah di sini.

231
00:14:26,999 --> 00:14:27,999
Tak berani berlawan?

232
00:14:28,638 --> 00:14:29,319
Kenapa?

233
00:14:29,718 --> 00:14:31,518
Takut saya mengecam identiti awak?

234
00:14:48,158 --> 00:14:49,359
Kuatnya kuasa rohani ini.

235
00:14:49,478 --> 00:14:50,038
Tunggu saya di sini.

236
00:14:50,038 --> 00:14:50,718
Saya pergi tengok.

237
