awak muncul di depan saya pula.

240
00:14:56,958 --> 00:14:58,119
Dewa Syaitan sekarang

241
00:14:58,359 --> 00:14:59,718
tak perlu saya takut lagi.

242
00:15:08,158 --> 00:15:09,038
Siapa?

243
00:15:09,199 --> 00:15:10,319
